Title: Windows service waits for network service during start
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1591082619
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

During the start Windows Agent service waits for network up to 30 seconds.

This may help to prevent strange errors if some plugins require network 
services available.

Value 30 second is default and may be changed in config file using parameter
<tt>system.wait_network</tt>
